Robert Half is currently recruiting a Reporting Systems Analyst to join a multinational.
Our client is a world-leading provider of sustainable productivity solutions.
The scope of responsibilities for this job include:
You support the monthly reporting process by ensuring smooth data flow from various systems;
You serve as first point of contact for finance users in the group;
You solve various issues raised by Finance users via virtual Service Desk;
